<!doctype html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="author" content="TGoC_Charlie and Bootstrap">
    <title>成功電研社-活動</title>


    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
    <%- include('./model/head.ejs') %>

    <style>
        #ahover:hover {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .bd-placeholder-img {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            text-anchor: middle;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .bd-placeholder-img-lg {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
        }

        @keyframes acheading {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            60% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .acheading {
            animation-name: acheading;
            animation-duration: 4s;
        }

        @keyframes right {
            from {
                position: relative;
                left: 30%;
            }
            to {
                left: -25%;
            }
        }

        @keyframes left {
            from {
                position: relative;
                right: 30%;
            }
            to {
                right: -25%;
            }
        }

        .summer, .class {
            animation-name: right;
            animation-duration: 7s;
        }

        .new, .fall {
            animation-name: left;
            animation-duration: 7s;
        }

        @keyframes main {
            from {
                position: relative;
                margin-top: -1500px;
            }
            to {
                margin-top: 0;
            }
        }

        main {
            animation-name: main;
            animation-duration: 5s;
        }

        @keyframes body {
            0% {
                overflow-y: hidden;
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }
            99% {
                overflow-y: hidden;
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }
            100% {
                overflow-y: auto;
                overflow-x: auto;
            }
        }

        body {
            animation-name: body;
            animation-duration: 2.5s;
        }
    </style>
    <!-- Custom styles for this template -->
    <script>
        window.onbeforeunload = function () {
            window.scrollTo(0, 0);
        }</script>
</head>

<body>
<%- include('./model/header.ejs') %>
<main role="main">


    <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
================================================== -->
    <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

    <div class="container marketing">

        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->


        <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

        <h1 class="featurette-heading col-12 acheading"
            style="text-align: center;margin-top: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;font-weight: bold;padding-top: 100px">
            活動</h1>
        <p class="acheading" style="font-size: x-large ; text-align: center">相信各位在社團只有打程式一定也很無聊，<br>
            所以我們會定期舉辦跨校的社團活動，讓你不只學會程式語言，<br>
            也結交外校的好朋友，豐富你的社團生活。</p>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette summer">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">暑訓</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:建中資訊、成功電研、中山資研、景美電資<br>
                    活動時間:8/3~8/9，為期7天(不過夜)<br>
                    活動內容:大地遊戲、主題式課程、企業參訪、RPG、成果發表、神秘活動<br>
                    參加對象:國三升高一學生為主，限40名</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/summer.png">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette new">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">迎新</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:成功電研、中山資研、建中電研、附中電算、大安電研、麗山星創、中和資研、政附資訊<br>
                    活動時間:10/18，為期1天<br>
                    活動內容:破冰遊戲、大地遊戲、演講、RPG<br>
                    參加對象:八校高一社員，人數不限</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/2020new.png">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette class">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">聯課</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:建中資訊、成功電研、中山資研、景美電資<br>
                    活動時間:10/31、11/1、11/7、11/8，為期4天<br>
                    活動內容:大地遊戲、主題式課程、RPG<br>
                    參加對象:四校高一社員，限40人</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/2020class.JPG">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette fall">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">秋遊</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:成功電研、景美電資<br>
                    活動時間:12/6<br>
                    活動內容:每年不定<br>
                    參加對象:兩校高一社員，人數不限</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/fall.jpeg">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette santa">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">耶晚</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:建中資訊、成功電研、中山資研、景美電資<br>
                    活動時間:12/25<br>
                    活動內容:交換禮物、團康<br>
                    參加對象:四校高一社員，人數不限</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/xmas.JPG">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette winter">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">寒訓</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:建中資訊、成功電研、中山資研、景美電資<br>
                    活動時間:2/2~2/8，為期7天(不過夜)<br>
                    活動內容:大地遊戲、主題式課程、RPG、成果發表、神秘活動<br>
                    參加對象:四校高一社員，限40人</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/winter.png">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette spring">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="featurette-heading">春遊</h2>
                <p class="lead">主辦學校:成功電研、中山資研<br>
                    活動時間:約三月初，為期1天<br>
                    活動內容：每年不定<br>
                    參加對象:兩校高一社員，人數不限</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img style="width: 100%;border-radius: 10px" src="assets/css/images/white.png">
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

